articles.description: The mega-marsquake, which is 5 times stronger than the previous record, may be the last big find from the InSight Mars Lander.
articles.content:
A Marsquake detected by NASA's InSight lander in May this year was at least five times larger than the next largest seismic event recorded on the planet.
